	<presentation id="index">
		<title>CAM API Compass: Get Your Bearings on Your API Journey</title>
		<toc class="abstract">Getting started and maintaining momentum with an API strategy can be a challenging task, with many moving and constantly evolving parts along the way. Continuous API Management (CAM) provides a structured look at the lifecycle on individual APIs, as well as on the overall API landscape and how it evolves over time. The CAM API Compass uses the concepts of lifecycle pillars and landscape aspects to provide a structured assessment of the status of individual APIs and the overall landscape. The CAM API Compass can help API developers and API architects to gain a better understanding of their API maturity, and where to best invest to improve their strategy and execution.</toc>
		<author><a href="http://dret.net/netdret/">Erik Wilde</a> <a href="http://twitter.com/dret" class="twitter-follow-button" data-size="large" title="Erik Wilde on Twitter: @dret">(<code>@dret</code>)</a></author>
